'''HD 97048'''，或稱為'''蝘蜓座CU'''，是一顆位於[[蝘蜓座|蝘蜓座]]的恆星，距離地球約500光年<ref name=ESO>{{Cite web |url=https://www.eso.org/public/images/eso1640c/ |title=Disc around the star HD 97048 |accessdate=2016-12-09 |archive-date=2016-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161120222501/http://www.eso.org/public/images/eso1640c/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 

== 星周盤==
HD 97048這顆年輕恆星已發現[[星周盤|星周盤]]的存在，2007年時以中紅外線波段觀測時發現盤內存在[[多環芳香烴|多環芳香烴]]<ref name=
Doucet>{{cite journal|bibcode=2007A&A...470..625D|title=HD 97048: a closer look at the disk|journal=Astronomy and Astrophysics|volume=470|display-authors=etal|author1=
Doucet|first1=C.|last2==Habart|first2=E.|year=2007}}</ref>。2016年時天文學家以裝設於[[欧洲南方天文台|欧洲南方天文台]][[甚大望遠鏡|甚大望遠鏡]]的{{link-en|光譜偏振高對比度系外行星研究儀|Spectro-Polarimetric High-Contrast Exoplanet Research}}（Spectro-Polarimetric High-Contrast Exoplanet Research，SPHERE）對HD 97048進行觀測，發現盤內已經形成同心圓狀的環結構<ref name=AstronomyNow>{{Cite web |url=https://astronomynow.com/2016/11/09/sphere-reveals-protoplanetary-discs-being-shaped-by-newborn-planets/ |title=SPHERE reveals protoplanetary discs being shaped by newborn planets |accessdate=2016-12-09 |archive-date=2016-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220110629/https://astronomynow.com/2016/11/09/sphere-reveals-protoplanetary-discs-being-shaped-by-newborn-planets/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

